title: Territory M no Juunin
original_name: テリトリー M の住人
sinopse:
Ema Okunishi is a freshman freshman who has come to a new city because of her parents' divorce. Still traumatized by the divorce, she can not get used to her new school and start conversation with her new classmates. One day Ema will visits a restaurant in the neighborhood and have an unexpected meeting...

(Source: MU)
